text: Víctor Pinto DT de Sol del Este en 2017 Víctor Pinto is a Paraguayan former association football player and current coach for Club Deportivo Sol del Este in the Paraguayan Tercera División. He played in the Primera División Paraguaya for Club 12 de Octubre with Dario Veron and Salvador Cabañas. ==References== Category:Paraguayan footballers Category:Living people Category:12 de Octubre footballers Category:Paraguayan football managers Category:Association footballers not categorized by position Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
